'''[[以色列|以色列]]和[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿拉伯联合酋长国]]'''于2020年8月13日正式'''建立关系'''，阿拉伯联合酋长国承认以色列为国家，两国建立了公共外交和经济关系。阿联酋成为繼[[埃及|埃及]]和[[约旦|约旦]]之后，阿拉伯国家中第三个（不計算有爭議的[[巴勒斯坦自治政府|巴勒斯坦自治政府]]）与以色列关系正常化的国家<ref name=新華社>{{cite news |title=以航将飞阿联酋　据信途经沙特领空 |url=https://www.sohu.com/a/415769464_267106 |publisher=新華社}}</ref>。阿联酋允许以色列公民进入阿联酋，反之阿联酋公民也可以进入以色列。<ref name=overflights>{{Cite web |url=http://www.universalweather.com/blog/united-arab-emirates-uae-landing-and-overflight-permit-requirements/ |title=OVERFLIGHT PERMIT REQUIREMENTS |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2019-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617231959/http://www.universalweather.com/blog/united-arab-emirates-uae-landing-and-overflight-permit-requirements/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>以色列和阿联酋之间没有直飞航班（截至2020年8月），因此所有的旅行暂时必须通过第三国（如约旦），但两国已同意启动机场之间的直飞。<ref name=tips/> 近年来，两国的非官方关系明显升温，双方在共同反对伊朗核计划和地区影响力的基础上开展了广泛的非官方合作。<ref name="newyorker"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.khaleejtimes.com/region/mena/video-tel-avivs-city-hall-lights-up-in-uae-israel-flags-to-celebrate-peace-deal |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814223357/https://www.khaleejtimes.com/region/mena/video-tel-avivs-city-hall-lights-up-in-uae-israel-flags-to-celebrate-peace-deal |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，由于COVID-19大流行，许多航空公司停止运营。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://theconversation.com/coronavirus-is-hurting-airlines-but-they-shouldnt-rush-to-cut-jobs-142943 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2020-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819144008/https://theconversation.com/coronavirus-is-hurting-airlines-but-they-shouldnt-rush-to-cut-jobs-142943 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年，以色列在阿布扎比向[[国际可再生能源机构|国际可再生能源机构]]设立了一个官方外交使团。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-1.688235?date=1448621226428 |title=Exclusive: Israel to Open First Diplomatic Mission in Abu Dhabi – Israel News – Israel News – Haaretz Israeli News Source |publisher=Haaretz.com |date=2015-11-27 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |newspaper=Haaretz |last1=Ravid |first1=Barak |archive-date=2018-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180111052723/https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-1.688235?date=1448621226428 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Weinglass |first=Simona |url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/in-diplomatic-first-israel-to-open-mission-in-abu-dhabi/ |title=In diplomatic first, Israel to open mission in Abu Dhabi |publisher=The Times of Israel |date= |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archive-date=2019-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190211181823/http://www.timesofisrael.com/in-diplomatic-first-israel-to-open-mission-in-abu-dhabi/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/why-israel-is-strengthening_b_11946660|title=Israel Is Strengthening Its Ties With The Gulf Monarchies|date=2016-09-12|website=HuffPost|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529083340/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/why-israel-is-strengthening_b_11946660|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年8月13日，以色列和阿联酋同意启动两国关系正常化。<ref name="2020relations">{{Cite news|date=2020-08-13|title=Israel and UAE strike historic peace deal|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-53770859|access-date=2020-08-13|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813152232/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-53770859|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月31日，兩國之間首條商業航班開通<ref name=新華社/>。
==历史==
===伊朗问题===
2009年美国总统奥巴马就职后，以色列和阿联酋驻美国大使在与即将上任的美国政府中东事务顾问举行的会议上共同呼吁，敦促美国对伊朗采取更强硬的立场。<ref name="newyorker">''New Yorker'', 16 June 2018, [https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2018/06/18/donald-trumps-new-world-order Donald Trump’s New World Order] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2018/06/18/donald-trumps-new-world-order |date=20180611112529 }}</ref>奥巴马在签署全面协议后取消了对伊朗的制裁。<ref>Maya Rhodan, [http://time.com/3956880/iran-nuclear-deal/ "Western Powers Reach Long-sought Nuclear Deal With Iran"] {{Wayback|url=http://time.com/3956880/iran-nuclear-deal/ |date=20190610114104 }}, ''Time'' (14 July 2015).</ref>

2012年9月，以色列总理[[内塔尼亚胡|内塔尼亚胡]]在纽约会见了阿联酋外长[[阿卜杜拉·本·扎耶德·阿勒纳哈扬|阿卜杜拉·本·扎耶德·阿勒纳哈扬]]。虽然他们同意共同对抗伊朗的威胁，但阿联酋拒绝公开改善关系，除非巴以和平进程取得进展。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/netanyahu-secretly-met-with-uae-foreign-minister-in-2012-in-new-york-1.5432342|title=Exclusive: Netanyahu Secretly Met With UAE Foreign Minister in 2012 in New York|website=Haaretz|date=2017-07-25|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2018-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207135229/https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/netanyahu-secretly-met-with-uae-foreign-minister-in-2012-in-new-york-1.5432342|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年，以色列驻美国大使罗恩·德尔默向阿联酋驻美大使优素福·奥泰巴通报了以色列反对[[联合全面行动计划|联合全面行动计划]]的态度，并敦促阿联酋在反对该协议方面发挥更积极的作用。<ref name="newyorker"/>

在奥巴马第二个总统任期即将结束之际，美国情报机构获悉两国官员之间的电话通话，包括内塔尼亚胡与一名阿联酋高级领导人之间的通话，以及内塔尼亚胡与阿联酋领导人在塞浦路斯举行的会议，会议的重点是合作打击伊朗。<ref name="newyorker"/>

[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]当选美国总统后，以色列和阿联酋都游说美国和俄罗斯恢复友好关系，以遏制伊朗对叙利亚的影响。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/israeli-saudi-and-emirati-officials-privately-pushed-for-trump-to-strike-a-grand-bargain-with-putin|title=Israeli, Saudi, and Emirati Officials Privately Pushed for Trump to Strike a "Grand Bargain" with Putin|website=The New Yorker|date=2018-07-09|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2018-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710042447/https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/israeli-saudi-and-emirati-officials-privately-pushed-for-trump-to-strike-a-grand-bargain-with-putin|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年6月，泄露的电子邮件显示，阿联酋和沙特阿拉伯与以色列合作对抗伊朗。为了“找到阻碍伊朗与世界各地大公司开展商业活动的途径”，阿联酋与[[保卫民主基金会|保卫民主基金会]]建立了密切关系。保卫民主基金会是一个亲以色列的新保守主义智库，也因其对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普政府的影响力而闻名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://217.218.67.231/Detail/2017/06/03/524103/UAE-Israel-Iran|title=Report says UAE envoy, pro-Israel think tank working against Iran|website=PressTV|date=2017-06-03|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813153536/http://217.218.67.231/Detail/2017/06/03/524103/UAE-Israel-Iran|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>''The Intercept'', 3 June 2017, [https://theintercept.com/2017/06/03/hacked-emails-show-top-uae-diplomat-coordinating-with-pro-israel-neocon-think-tank-against-iran/ Hacked Emails Show Top UAE Diplomat Coordinating With Pro-Israel Think Tank Against Iran] {{Wayback|url=https://theintercept.com/2017/06/03/hacked-emails-show-top-uae-diplomat-coordinating-with-pro-israel-neocon-think-tank-against-iran/ |date=20200813153545 }}</ref>

2017年7月，在阿联酋斡旋下，以色列情报部门与[[利比亚国民军|利比亚国民军]]司令[[哈利法·贝加斯姆·哈夫塔尔|哈利法·哈夫塔爾]]举行了会谈，以谈判以色列对哈夫塔尔部队的军事援助。利比亚国民军在[[第二次利比亞內戰|第二次利比亞內戰]]中得到了阿联酋的支持。<ref>''al Araby'', 24 July 2017, [https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2017/7/24/libyas-haftar-provided-with-israeli-weaponry-following-uae-mediated-meetings Libya's Haftar 'provided with Israeli military aid following UAE-mediated meetings with Mossad agents'] {{Wayback|url=https://www.alaraby.co.uk/english/news/2017/7/24/libyas-haftar-provided-with-israeli-weaponry-following-uae-mediated-meetings |date=20200226111741 }}</ref>

2018年3月，内塔尼亚胡在华盛顿特区的一家餐厅会见了奥泰巴和巴林驻美国大使，讨论了伊朗问题。<ref>''The Times of Israel'', [https://www.timesofisrael.com/dinner-diplomacy-netanyahus-unusual-encounter-with-uae-envoy/ Dinner diplomacy revealed: Netanyahu’s genial encounter with UAE, Bahrain envoys] {{Wayback|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/dinner-diplomacy-netanyahus-unusual-encounter-with-uae-envoy/ |date=20200813153547 }}</ref>

2018年10月10日，德尔默和奥泰巴在美国犹太国家安全学院年度晚宴上同桌交谈。<ref>''Haaretz'', [https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-israel-s-u-s-envoy-shares-table-with-uae-counterpart-in-sign-of-warming-ties-1.6548090 Israel's U.S. Envoy Shares Dinner Table With UAE Counterpart in Rare Sign of Warming Ties] {{Wayback|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-israel-s-u-s-envoy-shares-table-with-uae-counterpart-in-sign-of-warming-ties-1.6548090 |date=20200727071810 }}</ref>

