2018年9月，阿联酋在阿布扎比举行了以色列和土耳其官员秘密会谈，讨论恢复两国关系。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.middleeastmonitor.com/20180917-israel-turkey-hold-secret-talks-in-uae/|title=Israel, Turkey hold secret talks in UAE|website=Middle East Monitor|date=2018-09-17|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2020-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321222906/https://www.middleeastmonitor.com/20180917-israel-turkey-hold-secret-talks-in-uae/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年4月，以色列宣布已受邀参加迪拜2020年世博会创新博览会。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20190425-israel-take-part-dubai-expo-2020|title=Israel to take part in Dubai Expo 2020|work=France24|date=2019-04-25|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216224852/https://www.france24.com/en/20190425-israel-take-part-dubai-expo-2020|dead-url=no}}</ref>

