==2020年亚伯拉罕协定==
{{main|以阿和平协议}}
8月13日，以色列和阿联酋在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的斡旋下签署了一项协议。<ref name="2020relations"/>根据和平协议，以色列和阿联酋将建立全面外交关系，阿联酋将成为第三个承认以色列的阿拉伯国家。作为协议的一部分，以色列同意暂停[[吞并约旦河谷|吞并约旦河谷]]的计划。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/israel-uae-announce-normalisation-relations-200813145645861.html |title=Israel and UAE announce normalisation of relations with US help |work=Aljazeera |date=2020-08-13 |accessdate=2020-08-13 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813165717/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/israel-uae-announce-normalisation-relations-200813145645861.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

8月29日，阿联酋总统宣布废除该国1972年颁布的抵制以色列的有关法案<ref>{{cite news |title=阿联酋宣布废除抵制以色列法案 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-08/29/c_1126429549.htm |accessdate=2020-08-30 |archive-date=2020-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200912233402/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-08/29/c_1126429549.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

9月15日，两国在白宫签和平协议。这是以色列建国以来，第三份与阿拉伯国家达成的和平协议<ref>{{cite news |title=以色列和阿联酋建交 9月中将在白宫签和平协议 |url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%9C/20200908-%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E5%92%8C%E9%98%BF%E8%81%94%E9%85%8B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%A4-9%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AB%E7%AD%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE |accessdate=2020-09-10 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920063058/https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%9C/20200908-%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E5%92%8C%E9%98%BF%E8%81%94%E9%85%8B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%A4-9%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AB%E7%AD%BE%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 事件 ==
2010年1月19日，[[卡桑旅|卡桑旅]]的创立者Mahmoud al-Mabhouh在迪拜遭到暗杀，导致阿联酋呼吁通过国际刑警组织逮捕以色列摩萨德局长Meir Dagan。以色列既没有否认也没有证实与此事有关。迪拜警察局长塔米姆表示，所有被怀疑是以色列人的游客都不允许进入该国，即使他们持有外国护照。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2010/mar/01/dubai-police-bar-suspected-israelis |title=Dubai police chief bars all suspected Israelis entering UAE | World news |newspaper=The Guardian |date=March 2010 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813153531/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2010/mar/01/dubai-police-bar-suspected-israelis/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>事件发生后，阿联酋提议通过一项协议来修复与以色列的秘密关系，即以色列将向阿联酋提供武装无人机，但这一提议遭到了以色列的拒绝，因为它担心这会引起美国的反对。<ref name="newyorker"/>
==旅行==
在阿联酋没有正式承认以色列时，阿联酋禁止以色列公民或被怀疑是以色列公民的人进入阿联酋，包括以色列护照持有人，但允许转机。但是，允许护照上有以色列印章或签证的第三方国民入境。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice/united-arab-emirates/entry-requirements|title=Entry requirements – United Arab Emirates travel advice|website=GOV.UK|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805185651/https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice/united-arab-emirates/entry-requirements|dead-url=no}}</ref>以色列和阿联酋之间没有直飞航班，因此所有航班必须在第三个中立国(如约旦)停留，<ref name=tips>{{Cite web|url=https://traveltips.usatoday.com/way-travel-israel-dubai-uae-32934.html|title=The Best Way to Travel From Israel to Dubai, UAE|website=Travel Tips – USA Today|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2019-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617230153/https://traveltips.usatoday.com/way-travel-israel-dubai-uae-32934.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>以色列飞机也不允许进入阿联酋领空。<ref name="overflights"/>尽管阿联酋禁止其公民和飞机进入以色列，但这些限制在以色列并不适用。Mahbouh在迪拜被暗杀后，阿联酋加强了对以色列公民入境的限制，因为这件事被认为是以色列情报部门所为。<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/israelis-no-longer-allowed-in-dubai-after-hamas-hit-1.263926 |title='Israelis No Longer Allowed in Dubai After Hamas Hit' – Israel News – Haaretz Israeli News Source |publisher=Haaretz.com |date=2010-03-01 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710172656/https://www.haaretz.com/1.5035067 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年，澳洲航空与阿联酋航空达成了一项协议，让澳洲航空的航班在澳大利亚飞往欧洲的航班中停靠迪拜。<ref name=QantasStopover>{{Cite web|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-08-31/qantas-extends-emirates-partnership-and-ditches-dubai-london-st/8859790|title=Qantas extends Emirates deal and drops Dubai for Singapore stopover|date=2017-08-31|website=www.abc.net.au|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703112416/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2017-08-31/qantas-extends-emirates-partnership-and-ditches-dubai-london-st/8859790|dead-url=no}}</ref>有人担心，阿联酋的旅行限制将如何影响澳航的以色列国民或持以色列护照旅行的乘客，例如，如果这些乘客必须在迪拜过夜才能转机。澳航于2018年取消了该协议。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.news.com.au/travel/travel-advice/flights/qantas-stopovers-singapore-replaces-dubai-for-europe-flights/news-story/2c78df127267d3c9eb6ef02ab2c25fdd|title=Singapore replaces Dubai for Europe flights with Qantas|date=2018-04-12|website=NewsComAu|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2019-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014022626/https://www.news.com.au/travel/travel-advice/flights/qantas-stopovers-singapore-replaces-dubai-for-europe-flights/news-story/2c78df127267d3c9eb6ef02ab2c25fdd|dead-url=no}}</ref>

然而，在阿联酋有犹太侨民，也有拥有双重国籍的以色列人，他们以其他国家公民的身份在阿联酋居住、访问和工作。<ref name="Israelis"/>一些以色列公司通过第三方间接在阿联酋开展业务。<ref name="Israelis">{{cite web |last=Friedman |first=Ron |url=http://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Israelis-doing-business-in-Dubai-will-wait-out-storm |title=Israelis doing business in Dubai will wait out storm – Middle East – Jerusalem Post |publisher=Jpost.com |date= |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archive-date=2019-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620000951/https://www.jpost.com/Middle-East/Israelis-doing-business-in-Dubai-will-wait-out-storm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年6月，阿联酋阿提哈德航空公司在本古里安机场着陆，运送了一批医疗用品，帮助巴勒斯坦人应对COVID-19疫情。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.timesofisrael.com/second-uae-plane-carrying-virus-aid-for-palestinians-lands-in-israel/|title=Second UAE plane carrying virus aid for Palestinians lands in Israel|website=The Times of Israel|date=2020-06-09|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2020-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721125733/https://www.timesofisrael.com/second-uae-plane-carrying-virus-aid-for-palestinians-lands-in-israel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>当月晚些时候，以色列宣布与阿联酋建立伙伴关系，在各自国家合作应对COVID-19大流行。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/25/world/middleeast/israel-united-arab-emirates-coronavirus.html|title=Israel Announces Partnership With U.A.E., Which Throws Cold Water On It|website=The New York Times|date=2020-06-25|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2020-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625160029/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/25/world/middleeast/israel-united-arab-emirates-coronavirus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

